<div style="font-size: 16px; width: 800px" class="container">

  <h1>Concept</h1>

  <p><strong>postvite</strong> increases the value of presenting a poster at a conference by giving presenters the opportunity to personally invite any attendee to visit their poster. Before the conference, all presenters recieve an email directing them to a webpage to select attendees to invite. A few days later, attendees are sent a compilation of all of their invitations.</p>

  <h1>Usage</h1>

  <ol>
  	<li>Sign in with Google</li>
  	<li>Create a new conference</li>
  	<li>Upload attendee and presenter data</li>
  	<li>Let presenters select attendees to invite</li>
  	<li>Return later to send invitations</li>
  	<li>Done!</li>
  </ol>

